# Lockfile intentionally not tracked — this repo gets touched from
# both macOS and Linux sandboxes; cross-platform optional-dependency
# resolution (lightningcss native binaries) breaks when a Linux-generated
# lockfile is applied on macOS. Each environment generates its own.
# Vercel will produce one at build time.
